## ğŸ“Š Color Palette:

### Background Colors:
```
Card Background:     #FAFAFA (Light gray)
Info Box:           #F0F7FF (Light blue)
Pattern Card:       #F5F5F5 (Very light gray)
```

### Accent Colors:
```
Primary Blue:       #4A90E2 (Headers, badges)
High (Green):       #4CAF50 (Success)
Medium (Blue):      #4A90E2 (Info)
Low (Orange):       #FF9800 (Warning)
```

### Text Colors:
```
Headers:            #4A90E2 (Primary Blue)
Body Text:          #333333 (Dark Gray)
Descriptions:       #666666 (Medium Gray)
White Text:         #FFFFFF (On colored backgrounds)
```

---

## ğŸ“ Layout Improvements:

### Spacing:
- **Card Padding**: 15px all around
- **Between Cards**: 20px
- **Line Spacing**: 2pt in descriptions
- **Section Spacing**: 35px

### Typography Scale:
```
Page Header:        26pt (Bold)
Score Number:       42pt (Bold) - Big and bold!
Section Headers:    18pt (Bold)
Parameter Names:    15pt (Bold)
Sub-headers:        13pt (Bold)
Body Text:          10pt (Regular)
Descriptions:       9pt (Regular)
Small Text:         8pt (Regular)
```

### Visual Hierarchy:
1. **Most Important**: Large score number (42pt)
2. **Section Headers**: Medium size (18-26pt)
3. **Parameter Names**: Clear bold (15pt)
4. **Details**: Readable size (9-10pt)

